{"tid":2418411,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個細個會挽嘅嘢","createTime":"2021-02-22T14:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T16:59:14.000Z","uid":371347,"like":6,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"18aa4244774c10c578bb78b1247e12a0aef39d76","tid":2418411,"uid":371347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"最近去返自己大個嘅地方<br />\n啲童年回憶返晒嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想問下大家細個有咩好有童趣嘅遊戲會挽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拋磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 喺張紙上面畫咗個心目中嘅理想國出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後同鄰居小朋友拎啲鎖匙扣嘅公仔自言自語、角色扮演<br />\n<br />\n2. 屋村公園上面有好多用塗改液寫嘅mk嘢<br />\n我呢啲乖仔就當然冇寫<br />\n但成日望到都覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩到此一遊啊、xxx係個大仆街、aa鐘意bb、一生一世.........<br />\n<br />\n3. 屋企公園有啲成條水管咁嘅滑梯<br />\n就一定係調轉頭返上去行㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 同其他小朋友除晒衫浸嗰啲充氣水池<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 小學小息唔俾上班房<br />\n但就死都要避過晒啲風紀<br />\n然後匿係老師枱下面避過訓導主任<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 商場噴氣落玻璃畫公仔<br />\n然後俾保安話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗返都覺得好窩心<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為一個零零後<br />\n多謝阿爸阿媽唔係淨係送我去補習社渡過自己童年<br />\n依家啲小朋友勁慘細細個已經好chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家又有咩好正嘅童年回憶分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4310d068dcaa36d98eb27f78c249e6d64d5d62","tid":2418411,"uid":99305,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T14:56:09.000Z","msg":"挽你老母"},{"pid":"135084f8837a48b5cfe677bcc5a1f2c7259eb31f","tid":2418411,"uid":46587,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-2